dct_description_sm:
This polygon data layer represents aldermanic wards for
Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 1896-1901. This data layer was created by staff at the
American Geographical Society Library using scans of maps owned by the City of
Milwaukee. This is the first version of the shapefiles representing the
aldermanic wards and districts. Prior to 1972 aldermanic districts were called
aldermanic wards. This detail is reflected in the naming of the files. The
dataset was originally published by the American Geographical Society Library in
2020.
